[SPEAKER_01] za formiranje mojih stavova,

705
00:30:34,319 --> 00:30:35,220
[SPEAKER_01] mojih uvjerenja,

706
00:30:35,220 --> 00:30:37,539
[SPEAKER_01] mojih vrijednosti u mome životu.

707
00:30:37,839 --> 00:30:39,180
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo bi mi potpuno isto

708
00:30:39,180 --> 00:30:40,420
