709
00:30:40,420 --> 00:30:41,819
[SPEAKER_01] sa nekim drugim muškarcem.

710
00:30:41,819 --> 00:30:44,160
[SPEAKER_01] Ili odi reci tati svome.

711
00:30:44,160 --> 00:30:45,660
[SPEAKER_01] Tata, ti si bio suvišan.

712
00:30:45,660 --> 00:30:47,480
[SPEAKER_01] I šta ti je rekao?

713
