730
00:31:15,299 --> 00:31:16,940
[SPEAKER_01] Kažu mama je uvijek prema nama

731
00:31:16,940 --> 00:31:17,680
[SPEAKER_01] ovakva, ovakva.

732
00:31:17,779 --> 00:31:19,339
[SPEAKER_01] ali ti si skroz nešto drugo.

733
00:31:19,339 --> 00:31:21,700
[SPEAKER_01] Nekad je nama tako paše

734
00:31:21,700 --> 00:31:23,259
[SPEAKER_01] to što si ti skroz drugačiji.

735
00:31:23,259 --> 00:31:24,720
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam, u nekim stvarima

736
00:31:24,720 --> 00:31:27,160
[SPEAKER_01] ovoga, ono, tipa opušteniji mama

737
00:31:27,160 --> 00:31:28,480
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek, ono, ne znam,

738
00:31:28,480 --> 00:31:29,880
[SPEAKER_01] do detalja.

739
00:31:29,880 --> 00:31:32,039
[SPEAKER_01] Do detalja sve nešto istjeruje.

740
00:31:32,039 --> 00:31:34,099
[SPEAKER_01] Tata onako, ne znam, više...

741
00:31:34,099 --> 00:31:35,359
[SPEAKER_01] Zvuči mi poznato.

742
00:31:35,359 --> 00:31:36,259
[SPEAKER_01] Ajmo biti zabavno.

743
00:31:36,259 --> 00:31:37,339
[SPEAKER_01] Ajde da je zabavno.

744
00:31:37,339 --> 00:31:39,200
[SPEAKER_01] Ajmo negdje, ajmo i tako.

745
00:31:39,200 --> 00:31:41,299
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, evo, samo jedan od malih primjera.

746
00:31:41,299 --> 00:31:44,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ali koliko je to sve, dakle, važno?

747
00:31:44,039 --> 00:31:44,960
[SPEAKER_01] Između ostaloga,

748
00:31:44,960 --> 00:31:47,059
[SPEAKER_01] konvencija UN-a

749
00:31:47,059 --> 00:31:48,079
[SPEAKER_01] o pravima djece.

750
00:31:48,079 --> 00:31:50,200
[SPEAKER_01] Ona govori nešto vrlo interesantno

751
00:31:50,200 --> 00:31:51,119
[SPEAKER_01] što se prešučuje.

752
00:31:51,119 --> 00:31:53,359
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, prilikom posvajanja

753
00:31:53,359 --> 00:31:56,099
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, mora se voditi računa

754
00:31:56,099 --> 00:31:57,980
[SPEAKER_01] da dijete ide u okruženje

755
00:31:57,980 --> 00:31:59,640
[SPEAKER_01] koje je najsličnije

756
00:31:59,640 --> 00:32:01,819
[SPEAKER_01] po kulturi, po vjeri,

757
00:32:01,819 --> 00:32:03,900
[SPEAKER_01] po svim karakteristikama,

758
00:32:03,900 --> 00:32:05,900
[SPEAKER_01] parametrima onog okruženja

759
00:32:05,900 --> 00:32:07,579
[SPEAKER_01] iz kojeg je dijete išlo.

760
00:32:07,579 --> 00:32:10,180
[SPEAKER_01] Kako može biti najsličnije

761
00:32:10,180 --> 00:32:12,599
[SPEAKER_01] okruženje između okruženja

762
00:32:12,599 --> 00:32:13,900
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je imalo tatu i mamu

763
00:32:13,900 --> 00:32:16,339
[SPEAKER_01] da od jedan put sada više nema tatu i mamu.

764
00:32:16,339 --> 00:32:17,539
[SPEAKER_01] Da nema te modele.

765
00:32:17,539 --> 00:32:19,119
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, sad sam baš pročitala

766
00:32:19,119 --> 00:32:21,019
[SPEAKER_00] jedan znanstveni rad

767
00:32:21,019 --> 00:32:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] tu u Hrvatskoj napravljeno

768
00:32:23,000 --> 00:32:23,460
[SPEAKER_00] o tome

769
00:32:23,460 --> 00:32:24,880
[SPEAKER_00] u stvari

770
00:32:24,880 --> 00:32:26,380
[SPEAKER_00] da, istraživalo se

771
00:32:26,380 --> 00:32:28,200
[SPEAKER_00] primjere

772
00:32:28,200 --> 00:32:30,079
[SPEAKER_00] udomljavanja Roma,

773
00:32:30,079 --> 00:32:30,900
[SPEAKER_00] romske djece

774
00:32:30,900 --> 00:32:32,740
[SPEAKER_00] od strane romskih parova

775
00:32:32,740 --> 00:32:33,740
[SPEAKER_00] i romskih obitelji.

776
00:32:33,740 --> 00:32:34,599
[SPEAKER_00] I sad su,

777
00:32:34,599 --> 00:32:36,319
[SPEAKER_00] to je ovo što ti kažeš.

778
00:32:36,319 --> 00:32:37,339
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, imaš jednu

779
00:32:37,339 --> 00:32:38,680
[SPEAKER_00] podgrupu

780
00:32:38,680 --> 00:32:39,720
[SPEAKER_00] unutar društva

781
00:32:39,720 --> 00:32:40,140
[SPEAKER_00] koja ima

782
00:32:40,140 --> 00:32:41,740
[SPEAKER_00] drugi jezik,

783
00:32:41,740 --> 00:32:42,359
[SPEAKER_00] drugu kulturu

784
00:32:42,359 --> 00:32:43,700
[SPEAKER_00] i sada što?

785
00:32:43,700 --> 00:32:45,279
[SPEAKER_00] Normalan sljedeći korak

786
00:32:45,279 --> 00:32:46,099
[SPEAKER_00] je da ti kaoš čeke.

787
00:32:46,099 --> 00:32:48,299
[SPEAKER_00] Za romsko djete bi doista bilo,

788
00:32:48,299 --> 00:32:49,619
[SPEAKER_00] ako bi bilo dovoljno obitelji,

789
00:32:49,619 --> 00:32:50,839
[SPEAKER_00] najbolje da ga podiže

790
00:32:50,839 --> 00:32:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] jedna dobro strukturirana,

791
00:32:52,539 --> 00:32:54,099
[SPEAKER_00] organizirana romska obitelj.

792
00:32:54,099 --> 00:32:55,500
[SPEAKER_01] Jasno, da ostane u onome

793
00:32:55,500 --> 00:32:57,079
[SPEAKER_01] i kulturnom milijevu

794
00:32:57,079 --> 00:32:58,539
[SPEAKER_01] iz kojega je djete proizvršenje.

795
00:32:58,539 --> 00:33:01,400
[SPEAKER_00] Kada gledamo ove zemlje Afričke

796
00:33:01,400 --> 00:33:02,359
[SPEAKER_00] u kojima se pomaže

797
00:33:02,359 --> 00:33:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] radi siromaštva djeci,

798
00:33:04,000 --> 00:33:05,079
[SPEAKER_00] u principu,

799
00:33:05,079 --> 00:33:06,259
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi s kojima,

800
00:33:06,259 --> 00:33:07,819
[SPEAKER_00] evo, sam ja bila u kontaktu,

801
00:33:07,819 --> 00:33:08,799
[SPEAKER_00] oni nisu,

802
00:33:08,799 --> 00:33:09,960
[SPEAKER_00] oni ne,

803
00:33:09,960 --> 00:33:11,160
[SPEAKER_00] nisu zato da

804
00:33:11,160 --> 00:33:12,660
[SPEAKER_00] da se posvajaju

805
00:33:12,660 --> 00:33:14,140
[SPEAKER_00] u Evropu ili Ameriku

806
00:33:14,140 --> 00:33:15,559
[SPEAKER_00] njihova djeca

807
00:33:15,559 --> 00:33:17,079
[SPEAKER_00] u nekom velikom broju.

808
00:33:17,079 --> 00:33:17,880
[SPEAKER_00] Oni, on kaže,

809
00:33:17,880 --> 00:33:18,859
[SPEAKER_00] čekaj, ovdje ljudi

810
00:33:18,859 --> 00:33:19,640
[SPEAKER_00] jesu siromašni,

811
00:33:19,640 --> 00:33:21,099
[SPEAKER_00] ali idemo im pomoć

812
00:33:21,099 --> 00:33:22,039
[SPEAKER_00] u njihovom siromaštvu,

813
00:33:22,099 --> 00:33:23,059
[SPEAKER_00] idemo ih podučiti,

814
00:33:23,059 --> 00:33:24,180
[SPEAKER_00] a ne da i mi uzimamo

815
00:33:24,180 --> 00:33:25,200
[SPEAKER_00] njihovu djecu.

816
00:33:25,200 --> 00:33:26,180
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, naravno da to

817
00:33:26,180 --> 00:33:27,019
[SPEAKER_00] isključuje ovi slučaje

818
00:33:27,019 --> 00:33:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] u kojima smo već rekli,

819
00:33:28,000 --> 00:33:29,559
[SPEAKER_00] nasilja, zlostavljanja.

820
00:33:29,559 --> 00:33:31,119
[SPEAKER_00] O tom nemamo što razgovara.

821
00:33:31,119 --> 00:33:32,259
[SPEAKER_00] To su djeca koju treba

822
00:33:32,259 --> 00:33:33,720
[SPEAKER_00] zaštititi, izuzeti.

823
00:33:33,720 --> 00:33:35,200
[SPEAKER_01] I u sustavu imamo te brojike

824
00:33:35,200 --> 00:33:36,900
[SPEAKER_01] koje govore o jednom broju

825
00:33:36,900 --> 00:33:37,940
[SPEAKER_01] izuzimanja,

826
00:33:37,940 --> 00:33:39,119
[SPEAKER_01] na taj način da se

827
00:33:39,119 --> 00:33:40,380
[SPEAKER_01] trenutno u sustavu

828
00:33:40,380 --> 00:33:41,119
[SPEAKER_00] u prosjeku je oko

829
00:33:41,119 --> 00:33:42,359
[SPEAKER_00] tri i pol tisuće djece.

830
00:33:42,359 --> 00:33:43,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, daj mi rijeci,

831
00:33:43,380 --> 00:33:44,160
[SPEAKER_00] ti si radio,

832
00:33:44,160 --> 00:33:45,440
[SPEAKER_00] opet sad da se vratimo

833
00:33:45,440 --> 00:33:47,119
[SPEAKER_00] i ovom modelu

834
00:33:47,119 --> 00:33:47,980
[SPEAKER_00] i ovom pitanju

835
00:33:47,980 --> 00:33:48,980
[SPEAKER_00] nasilja.

836
00:33:48,980 --> 00:33:49,519
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, nekako

837
00:33:49,519 --> 00:33:50,900
[SPEAKER_00] sad u ovim,

838
00:33:50,900 --> 00:33:53,059
[SPEAKER_00] u ovoj crno-bijeloj

839
00:33:53,059 --> 00:33:54,400
[SPEAKER_00] lici emocijonalnoj

840
00:33:54,400 --> 00:33:55,059
[SPEAKER_00] koja se stvoji,

841
00:33:55,059 --> 00:33:56,200
[SPEAKER_00] onda se postavi

842
00:33:56,200 --> 00:33:57,380
[SPEAKER_00] kao da bi trebalo

843
00:33:57,380 --> 00:33:58,599
[SPEAKER_00] poništiti nasilnika.

844
00:33:58,599 --> 00:33:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kao ono,

845
00:33:59,000 --> 00:33:59,980
[SPEAKER_00] prekrižimo ga,

846
00:33:59,980 --> 00:34:01,019
[SPEAKER_00] bacimo ga u crnu jamu.

847
00:34:01,019 --> 00:34:01,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da, nikako ne.

848
00:34:01,539 --> 00:34:03,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si radio jako puno,

849
00:34:03,240 --> 00:34:03,740
[SPEAKER_00] pa evo, daj,

850
00:34:03,740 --> 00:34:04,640
[SPEAKER_00] reci nam o tome.

851
00:34:04,660 --> 00:34:05,740
[SPEAKER_01] lijepa iskustva imao

852
00:34:05,740 --> 00:34:06,819
[SPEAKER_01] i jako sam zahvalan

853
00:34:06,819 --> 00:34:08,079
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, ljudima

854
00:34:08,079 --> 00:34:09,260
[SPEAKER_01] koji su mi to omogućili.

855
00:34:09,260 --> 00:34:10,079
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to je

856
00:34:10,079 --> 00:34:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] prije svega,

857
00:34:11,000 --> 00:34:12,199
[SPEAKER_01] evo, s našeg fakulteta

858
00:34:12,199 --> 00:34:15,739
[SPEAKER_01] profesorica Marina Eduković,

859
00:34:15,739 --> 00:34:17,659
[SPEAKER_01] njezin suprug Dejana Eduković

860
00:34:17,659 --> 00:34:20,920
[SPEAKER_01] sa rehabilitacijskog fakulteta

861
00:34:20,920 --> 00:34:23,119
[SPEAKER_01] i DPP,

862
00:34:23,119 --> 00:34:24,380
[SPEAKER_01] modus kao udruge.

863
00:34:24,380 --> 00:34:25,619
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su bili,

864
00:34:25,619 --> 00:34:27,280
[SPEAKER_01] pokrenuli edukaciju,

865
00:34:27,280 --> 00:34:28,179
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, mi smo stekli

866
00:34:28,179 --> 00:34:29,139
[SPEAKER_01] taj certifikat

867
00:34:29,139 --> 00:34:30,960
[SPEAKER_01] i preko modusa

868
00:34:30,960 --> 00:34:31,940
[SPEAKER_01] i DPP-a,

869
00:34:31,940 --> 00:34:33,659
[SPEAKER_01] društva za psihološku pomoć,

870
00:34:33,739 --> 00:34:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, sam bio uključen

871
00:34:35,000 --> 00:34:37,019
[SPEAKER_01] kao izvoditelj

872
00:34:37,019 --> 00:34:38,639
[SPEAKER_01] mjere psihosocijalnog tretmana

873
00:34:38,639 --> 00:34:40,159
[SPEAKER_01] počinitelja nasilja u bitelji,

874
00:34:40,159 --> 00:34:41,980
[SPEAKER_01] gdje prekrišajni sud,

875
00:34:41,980 --> 00:34:43,440
[SPEAKER_01] tada je to isključivo bila

876
00:34:43,440 --> 00:34:45,059
[SPEAKER_01] domena prekrišajnog suda,

877
00:34:45,059 --> 00:34:48,840
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, nasilje je vrlo široko definirano.

878
00:34:48,840 --> 00:34:51,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi obično misle da je to samo ovo fizičko,

879
00:34:51,539 --> 00:34:52,780
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, ili seksualno,

880
00:34:52,780 --> 00:34:55,699
[SPEAKER_01] ali to je pod psihološkim nasiljem

881
00:34:55,699 --> 00:34:56,699
[SPEAKER_01] svaka uvreda.

882
00:34:56,699 --> 00:34:58,219
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ono tamo definira,

883
00:34:58,219 --> 00:34:59,559
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam ako se osjeća da,

884
00:34:59,559 --> 00:35:02,019
[SPEAKER_01] ako se subjektivno osjeća žrtva

885
00:35:02,019 --> 00:35:04,099
[SPEAKER_01] da je povrijeđeno njezino dostojanstvo,

886
00:35:04,099 --> 00:35:05,420
[SPEAKER_01] da se osjećala uznemireno,

887
00:35:05,420 --> 00:35:07,440
[SPEAKER_01] radi nečega to može biti, ne znam,

888
00:35:07,440 --> 00:35:10,760
[SPEAKER_01] ono što povišeni tom,

889
00:35:10,760 --> 00:35:11,920
[SPEAKER_01] vikanje, ne znam,

890
00:35:11,920 --> 00:35:14,679
[SPEAKER_01] omalovažavanje pred prijateljima u društvu,

891
00:35:14,679 --> 00:35:16,739
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam, pričanje nekih anegdota

892
00:35:16,739 --> 00:35:18,780
[SPEAKER_01] koje ponižava vas, recimo,

893
00:35:18,780 --> 00:35:20,719
[SPEAKER_01] kao bračnog partnera pred nekime.

894
00:35:20,719 --> 00:35:23,639
[SPEAKER_01] Sve je to unutar definicije nasilja u obitelji.

895
00:35:23,639 --> 00:35:26,300
[SPEAKER_01] Radi svega toga ćeš ti završiti na prekrišenjem sudu.

896
00:35:26,300 --> 00:35:28,500
[SPEAKER_01] Za svaki, glupane, kravo,

897
00:35:28,500 --> 00:35:29,880
[SPEAKER_01] bilo šta, ne znam,

898
00:35:29,880 --> 00:35:31,400
[SPEAKER_01] psovke koje se izgovaraju.

899
00:35:31,400 --> 00:35:32,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ja mogu postaviti pitanje,

900
00:35:32,880 --> 00:35:34,980
[SPEAKER_01] i to sam postavio kad smo imali tu edukaciju,

901
00:35:34,980 --> 00:35:37,260
[SPEAKER_01] kažem, postoji li i jedna obitelj

902
00:35:37,260 --> 00:35:38,380
[SPEAKER_01] u Republici Hrvatskoj

903
00:35:38,380 --> 00:35:41,659
[SPEAKER_01] koja je izuzeta iz ove definicije nasilja?

904
00:35:41,659 --> 00:35:44,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ako vi pogledate da su psovke,

905
00:35:44,159 --> 00:35:46,199
[SPEAKER_01] sastavni dio filmova, kulture,

906
00:35:46,199 --> 00:35:50,059
[SPEAKER_01] antikulture u Hrvatskoj,

907
00:35:50,059 --> 00:35:51,840
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, gdje sam ja sa blažnjen,

908
00:35:51,840 --> 00:35:53,519
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam, osta isto na jednoj predstavi

909
00:35:53,519 --> 00:35:54,139
[SPEAKER_01] koju sam gledao,

910
00:35:54,139 --> 00:35:57,960
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, toliko brutalno se prostači, psuje.

911
00:35:57,960 --> 00:36:00,260
[SPEAKER_01] I te psovke su prisutne

912
00:36:00,260 --> 00:36:03,840
[SPEAKER_01] u jednom većem broju hrvatskih obitelji.

913
00:36:03,840 --> 00:36:06,980
[SPEAKER_01] Za svaku tu izgovorenu prostotu

914
00:36:06,980 --> 00:36:08,480
[SPEAKER_01] jedan drugome unutar kuće,

915
00:36:08,480 --> 00:36:09,760
[SPEAKER_01] svako vikanje,

916
00:36:09,760 --> 00:36:11,360
[SPEAKER_01] svaka ona ljutnja,

917
00:36:11,639 --> 00:36:13,320
[SPEAKER_01] svađa koja je, ne znam,

918
00:36:13,320 --> 00:36:14,780
[SPEAKER_01] sa povišenim tonovima,

919
00:36:14,780 --> 00:36:16,719
[SPEAKER_01] sve to ulazi u definiciju nasilja

920
00:36:16,719 --> 00:36:18,800
[SPEAKER_01] i sve bi to ti završio na sudu

921
00:36:18,800 --> 00:36:20,559
[SPEAKER_01] i sve bi to kao jedna od mjera

922
00:36:20,559 --> 00:36:22,179
[SPEAKER_01] koju sud može odrediti.

923
00:36:22,179 --> 00:36:24,179
[SPEAKER_01] Sud može odrediti, ne znam,

924
00:36:24,179 --> 00:36:25,880
[SPEAKER_01] da se izuzme,

925
00:36:25,880 --> 00:36:28,260
[SPEAKER_01] da ti više ne može živiti u tom kućanstvu,

926
00:36:28,260 --> 00:36:29,920
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, sud tebi može dati mjeru

927
00:36:29,920 --> 00:36:30,880
[SPEAKER_01] da se zaštiti,

928
00:36:30,880 --> 00:36:33,519
[SPEAKER_01] ako je sumnja da ćeš počiniti

929
00:36:33,519 --> 00:36:36,119
[SPEAKER_01] neko, recimo, fizičko ili neko kazneno dijelo,

930
00:36:36,119 --> 00:36:40,280
[SPEAKER_01] dalje može ti zabranu prilaska osobi odrediti

931
00:36:40,280 --> 00:36:43,539
[SPEAKER_01] i može ti dati psihosocijalni tretman po činitelj naslije.

932
00:36:43,539 --> 00:36:46,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ta mjera je, po meni, fenomenalna mjera,

933
00:36:46,539 --> 00:36:47,940
[SPEAKER_01] zato što doslovno svi...

934
00:36:47,940 --> 00:36:49,619
[SPEAKER_00] Da li ona sad postoji ili ne?

935
00:36:49,619 --> 00:36:51,300
[SPEAKER_01] Postoji, postoji, dakle...

936
00:36:51,300 --> 00:36:53,480
[SPEAKER_00] Neko vrijeme nije bilo, ako sam dobro bila uprati.

937
00:36:53,480 --> 00:36:55,559
[SPEAKER_01] Pa jedno vrijeme je ovako, dakle,

938
00:36:55,559 --> 00:36:58,099
[SPEAKER_01] postoja je problem sa ministarstvom pravosluđa

939
00:36:58,099 --> 00:36:59,980
[SPEAKER_01] oko definiranja cijene te usluge.

940
00:36:59,980 --> 00:37:02,199
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, provedene su edukacije,

941
00:37:02,199 --> 00:37:03,739
[SPEAKER_01] postojali su certifikati,

942
00:37:03,739 --> 00:37:05,900
[SPEAKER_01] zakon je predvidio i pravilnik,

943
00:37:05,900 --> 00:37:08,480
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, da vi onda trebate imati neke osnovne uvjete

944
00:37:08,480 --> 00:37:10,940
[SPEAKER_01] i možete se licencu tražiti od države.

945
00:37:11,019 --> 00:37:13,039
[SPEAKER_01] I onda sklapate ugovor sa ministarstvom

946
00:37:13,039 --> 00:37:16,739
[SPEAKER_01] gdje, nakon što zadovoljite osnovne uvjete,

947
00:37:16,739 --> 00:37:18,820
[SPEAKER_01] prostora, ne znam, on mora imat čekaonicu,

948
00:37:18,820 --> 00:37:20,599
[SPEAKER_01] sanitarni čvor, ne znam, i tu prostoriju

949
00:37:20,599 --> 00:37:22,639
[SPEAKER_01] gdje ćete raditi s njima, sa grupom.

950
00:37:22,639 --> 00:37:24,880
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, onda sklapate ugovor

951
00:37:24,880 --> 00:37:28,139
[SPEAKER_01] i sud ima informaciju da ste vi jedan od.

952
00:37:28,139 --> 00:37:30,539
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, njih je 2018. i 2019.

953
00:37:30,539 --> 00:37:33,980
[SPEAKER_01] ih je bilo 41, ta pravna i fizička osoba

954
00:37:33,980 --> 00:37:37,219
[SPEAKER_01] koja je to imala ugovore,

955
00:37:37,219 --> 00:37:40,780
[SPEAKER_01] a ima ih oko 80 koji su stekli uvjete.

956
00:37:41,019 --> 00:37:42,500
[SPEAKER_01] i koji imaju licencu.

957
00:37:42,500 --> 00:37:44,480
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, vidimo da već pola njih

958
00:37:44,480 --> 00:37:46,579
[SPEAKER_01] nije sklopilo ugovor sa ministarstvom,

959
00:37:46,579 --> 00:37:47,699
[SPEAKER_01] to je jedan dio problema.

960
00:37:47,699 --> 00:37:51,780
[SPEAKER_01] Drugo, tri županije nemaju tu uslugu,

961
00:37:51,780 --> 00:37:54,539
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, nema tko to provoditi u tri županije.

962
00:37:54,539 --> 00:37:56,019
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, raca po činiteljima.

963
00:37:56,019 --> 00:37:57,159
[SPEAKER_01] Raca po činiteljima.

964
00:37:57,159 --> 00:38:00,019
[SPEAKER_01] Tek nedavno su, ne znam, njih tri, četiri bile

965
00:38:00,019 --> 00:38:03,900
[SPEAKER_01] kao Zadarska, ne znam, Požeška i tako dalje.

966
00:38:03,900 --> 00:38:06,699
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, vi ste imali problem.

967
00:38:06,699 --> 00:38:09,639
[SPEAKER_01] S jedne strane, nije imao tko to odraditi na terenu,

968
00:38:10,179 --> 00:38:11,980
