970
00:38:14,260 --> 00:38:17,420
[SPEAKER_01] ili to rade, ajmo to reći, privatno.

971
00:38:17,420 --> 00:38:20,659
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ne znam, vi, željka, ti i ja,

972
00:38:20,659 --> 00:38:23,400
[SPEAKER_01] mi završimo, imamo licencu

973
00:38:23,400 --> 00:38:24,800
[SPEAKER_01] i odlučimo se baviti s time

974
00:38:24,800 --> 00:38:27,860
[SPEAKER_01] i podnesemo zahtjevi u nekom prostoru,

975
