[SPEAKER_01] radi kojega su došli,

989
00:38:58,320 --> 00:39:00,300
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda to umanjuju,

990
00:39:00,300 --> 00:39:04,139
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, to se relativiziraju i tako dalje,

991
00:39:04,139 --> 00:39:07,599
[SPEAKER_01] ali na početku potpišu

992
