[SPEAKER_01] iz kojih smo došli,

1082
00:42:09,219 --> 00:42:11,059
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, da ti sada

1083
00:42:11,059 --> 00:42:15,079
[SPEAKER_01] tome čovjeku na neki način,

1084
