[SPEAKER_01] psihosocijalnog tretmana

1100
00:42:42,139 --> 00:42:44,099
[SPEAKER_01] da se nasilje više ne ponovi.

1101
00:42:44,099 --> 00:42:45,860
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ne da se neće ponovi

1102
00:42:45,860 --> 00:42:47,059
[SPEAKER_01] time što ćeš ga u Sibiru

1103
00:42:47,059 --> 00:42:48,659
[SPEAKER_01] u neki tamo gulag ga staviti

1104
