[SPEAKER_01] i reći, evo sad on više nema

1105
00:42:50,340 --> 00:42:51,300
[SPEAKER_01] koga više tuć,

1106
00:42:51,300 --> 00:42:53,119
[SPEAKER_01] nego mogu li ja tog čovjeka

1107
00:42:53,119 --> 00:42:55,599
[SPEAKER_01] naučiti da on drugačije komunicira?

1108
00:42:55,599 --> 00:42:57,920
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, ono s čime sam krenuo,

1109
00:42:57,920 --> 00:43:00,300
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, oni su u početku otpor

1110
