1113
00:43:06,300 --> 00:43:08,099
[SPEAKER_01] To mi svi osjetimo.

1114
00:43:08,099 --> 00:43:10,280
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje na kraju od njih slušate,

1115
00:43:10,280 --> 00:43:12,420
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam imao baš

1116
00:43:12,420 --> 00:43:15,739
[SPEAKER_01] jako interesantne klijente

1117
